{"tid":2209090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國商務部公布《不可靠實體清單規定》，即日生效","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T11:33:25.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6965f8336976a9acfcb5d46e17c5388ab2378278","tid":2209090,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"《不可靠實體清單規定》合有14條，涵蓋「不可靠實體」的定義、監管、調查和處理措施等準則。<br />\n商務部指出，為維護國家主權、保護中國企業或個人合法權益，根據多項法律制定《不可靠實體清單規定》，規定指外國實體，包括外國企業、組織或個人，一旦收到舉報或建議，經調查後證實相關實體在國際經貿及活動中，危害中國國家主權、安全和發展利益，中國將採取相應措施，包括限制或禁止從事跟中國有關的進出口活動、限制或禁止在中國境內投資、限制或取消相關人員在中國境內工作許可停留或居貿資格等。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=406132&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406132%26refer%3DShare&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=eb641f91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406132%26refer%3DShare&h=1b51f582\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=406132&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"a8a31d664c1f6a95397d56ef134dd4be7fb40deb","tid":2209090,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">小丑蝈！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"}]}